* Yvon Collin (1988–1989)
* Émile Zuccarelli (1989–1992)
* Jean-François Hory (1992–1996)
* Jean-Michel Baylet (1996–2016)
* Sylvia Pinel (2016–2017)
* Guillaume Lacroix (2019–present)

